item.title: Shop Small with ProsperUS Detroit: Holiday Season 2016
item.description: ProsperUS November Networking Night Thursday, November 17, 2016, at 5:30 - 7:30 PM Vista Partnership / St. Anthony’s Church, 3555 Vernor Hwy, Detroit, MI 48216 Join the ProsperUS team for our monthly networking event for Graduates, current participants, prospective students, and friends! We will be featuring authentic Salvadoran cuisine from Cecilia Ardon of Bendicion de Dios and Juan Carlos from Featherstone Moments will do a presentation on revenue-generating “Holiday Marketing Ideas.
